{"tid":1850843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［藍到紅］可唔可以換走我個老豆老母","createTime":"2020-01-29T17:49:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T09:04:39.000Z","uid":202878,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"428c50714b9e6d803810518563d48ddbf6bdec5b","tid":1850843,"uid":202878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:49:31.000Z","msg":"話說兩老係藍絲 老豆就藍到紅個種<br />\n本身已經人一藍腦便殘<br />\n但至少藍絲係自私嘅 肺炎都識搶口罩用<br />\n<br />\n我唔喺香港 但一月頭已經叫屋企人買口罩<br />\n佢哋嗰陣仲喺到叫我洗乜緊張啊<br />\n結果真係爆發 我日日追住佢地嚟問有冇買口罩<br />\nSend曬啲消委會口罩測試資料俾佢哋<br />\n咁佢哋一直都話屋企有兩盒<br />\n咁我叫佢哋影相嚟<br />\n點撚知俾啲咁撚樣嘅嘢我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Fk5PXP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Fk5PXP.jpg&h=c64507a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WGpFDQ9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWGpFDQ9.jpg&h=a5cbaa97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1rorzpv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1rorzpv.jpg&h=3eb08e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMade in 湖北啊大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 另一盒就睇唔明<br />\n而家仲要周圍都冇口罩賣<br />\n連海外都冇<br />\n我就翻香港啦<br />\n我唔想死啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd8063dacf77510703612d40ff766717dc9ca45","tid":1850843,"uid":202878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:50:26.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫我換走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838deaa461dbbecb76986c3c091881bd3003298c","tid":1850843,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"醫護手足 點可以因為一場本可以封關避免嘅病毒而賭上生命<br />\n我地仲未光復到香港啊..<br />\nbtw p牌求推一推... <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥  借刀殺人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850782</a>"},{"pid":"2c83330049b5e0124ce0d70555245b17c6ef918d","tid":1850843,"uid":202878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"而家邊到有口罩賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc21eeac214acf7c9fcf90c8c5362b3639a376a1","tid":1850843,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:51:36.000Z","msg":"好過冇啦<br />\n用住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4647f4e0b4e15458561f329160c4a21e4e7e8bab","tid":1850843,"uid":50218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:51:58.000Z","msg":"排萬寧啦，"},{"pid":"16b7f734beea2456405c4258a215d0b4dca06b6d","tid":1850843,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a1f1c52969f68ff6b6aa0d0bc0b42a2da3db6f","tid":1850843,"uid":202878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cc21eeac214acf7c9fcf90c8c5362b3639a376a1","tid":1850843,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:51:36.000Z","msg":"好過冇啦<br />\n用住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:52:45.000Z","msg":"用咗仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自以爲冇事去同人接觸"},{"pid":"41491687847bc3d82998f87e8ed4865776b55f58","tid":1850843,"uid":258809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c83330049b5e0124ce0d70555245b17c6ef918d","tid":1850843,"uid":202878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"而家邊到有口罩賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:52:58.000Z","msg":"二月頭同中 應該會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo